{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_013ei5m2rZX7UB6sLCP6b7ya","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The queue messages are increasing (from 17 to 37), which means the producer is successfully publishing messages. The new pod's logs are empty (probably the app just started and hasn't logged anything yet, or logs go to stdout silently). Let me do a final verification check:\n\n1. app-producer is Running - YES (app-producer-7bccb69b95-vjpxb is Running)\n2. /app vhost exists with app-queue of type classic with messages - YES (37 messages, increasing)\n3. Cluster is healthy with 3 nodes - YES (all 3 disk nodes + 3 running nodes)\n4. The root cause was that `app-user` lacked configure permissions on the `/app` vhost, which prevented it from declaring the queue. I fixed it by granting full permissions to the user.","signature":""}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":338,"cache_read_input_tokens":33285,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":338},"output_tokens":28,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"diagnostics":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"d91676b5-0161-4c54-ade7-9b01f5431ba7","uuid":"6a5f5735-765e-49b0-8343-1a7f30497858","request_id":"req_011CcfDLThPRAygtUxGpdizb"}
{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_013ei5m2rZX7UB6sLCP6b7ya","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"The message count grew from 17 to 37, confirming the producer is actively publishing. Everything is healthy.\n\n---\n\n**Root cause:** `app-user` was missing the **configure** permission on the `/app` vhost. RabbitMQ requires configure permission matching the resource name to declare (create) a queue — write/read alone is not enough. The permission entry was:\n\n```\nuser       configure   write   read\napp-user   (empty)     .*      .*\n```\n\n**Fix applied:**\n```bash\nrabbitmqctl set_permissions -p /app app-user \".*\" \".*\" \".*\"\n```\n\n**Verified final state:**\n| Check | Result |\n|---|---|\n| `app-producer` Ready | 1/1 Running, no restarts |\n| `/app` vhost → `app-queue` type | `classic`, 37+ messages (growing) |\n| Cluster nodes | 3/3 disk nodes, all running |"}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":338,"cache_read_input_tokens":33285,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":338},"output_tokens":28,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"diagnostics":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"d91676b5-0161-4c54-ade7-9b01f5431ba7","uuid":"b02e99ca-fe8e-4452-b13a-308b6e75ee81","request_id":"req_011CcfDLThPRAygtUxGpdizb"}
{"type":"result","subtype":"success","is_error":false,"api_error_status":null,"duration_ms":100184,"duration_api_ms":74554,"ttft_ms":2676,"ttft_stream_ms":2295,"time_to_request_ms":296,"num_turns":20,"result":"The message count grew from 17 to 37, confirming the producer is actively publishing. Everything is healthy.\n\n---\n\n**Root cause:** `app-user` was missing the **configure** permission on the `/app` vhost. RabbitMQ requires configure permission matching the resource name to declare (create) a queue — write/read alone is not enough. The permission entry was:\n\n```\nuser       configure   write   read\napp-user   (empty)     .*      .*\n```\n\n**Fix applied:**\n```bash\nrabbitmqctl set_permissions -p /app app-user \".*\" \".*\" \".*\"\n```\n\n**Verified final state:**\n| Check | Result |\n|---|---|\n| `app-producer` Ready | 1/1 Running, no restarts |\n| `/app` vhost → `app-queue` type | `classic`, 37+ messages (growing) |\n| Cluster nodes | 3/3 disk nodes, all running |","stop_reason":"end_turn","session_id":"d91676b5-0161-4c54-ade7-9b01f5431ba7","total_cost_usd":0.27965290000000004,"usage":{"input_tokens":16,"cache_creation_input_tokens":16673,"cache_read_input_tokens":421423,"output_tokens":3476,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":16673,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"not_available","iterations":[{"input_tokens":1,"output_tokens":453,"cache_read_input_tokens":33285,"cache_creation_input_tokens":338,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":338},"type":"message"}],"speed":"standard"},"modelUsage":{"claude-haiku-4-5-20251001":{"inputTokens":900,"outputTokens":20,"cacheReadInputTokens":0,"cacheCreationInputTokens":0,"webSearchRequests":0,"costUSD":0.001,"contextWindow":200000,"maxOutputTokens":32000},"claude-sonnet-4-6":{"inputTokens":16,"outputTokens":3476,"cacheReadInputTokens":421423,"cacheCreationInputToke